                "text": "To compute the shipping cost, I will use the formula provided by the shipping-cost-skill:\n\n**Formula:**  \nShipping Cost = Base Rate + (Rate per kg × Package Weight)\n\nFor domestic shipping:\n- Base Rate = $5\n- Rate per kg = $2\n\nGiven:\n- Package Weight = 3 kg\n\nCalculation:\nShipping Cost = $5 + ($2 × 3)  \nShipping Cost = $5 + $6  \nShipping Cost = **$11**\n\n**The shipping cost for a 3 kg package shipped domestically is $11.**",
